 22.9304 43.5711 22.9304 43.5711 22.958C42.6324 23.8967 41.0587 24.7802 39.4574 25.2219C38.7396 25.4152 38.0218 25.5532 37.2764 25.5808C36.9727 25.6084 36.6414 25.6084 36.3101 25.6084C35.8683 25.6084 35.399 25.6084 34.9296 25.6636C33.5768 25.8293 32.2792 26.2986 31.0644 27.0441C29.4079 28.0656 27.9723 29.5565 27.1716 31.1301C26.2605 32.8695 25.9292 34.9677 26.1225 37.3421C26.1501 37.8114 26.2329 38.2808 26.3157 38.7501C26.4262 39.3023 26.509 39.9097 26.5366 40.4895C26.5918 42.2012 26.0673 43.8853 25.0457 45.3762C24.9905 45.4314 24.9905 45.5418 25.0181 45.6523Z" fill="#245A66" fill-opacity="0.8"/>
